
'''Eva Esselba Mends''' yɛ Ghanani a w'aben wɔ Sika ho ntotoe a ɛne ɛkɔnomise mu. ɔyɛ ɔbaa a odiakn a wɔpaw no sɛ okwakyerefo a oda sikasɛm ho ntotoeɛ ano wo adwumakuo a ɛde Ministry Of Finance wɔ Ghana. Aban no paw no wɔ afe 2017 mu.

== Nhomasua ==
ɔkɔɔ Suapɔn a ɛde University of Ghana kosuaa sikasɛm ho ntotoeɛ a ɛne ekɔnɔmise ne Political Science. Okuraa abɔdin krataa a ɛde Executive Master's degree in  firii Public Administration onyaa firii suapɔn a ɛde Ghana Institute of Management and Public administration. Osuaa nnema nkenkete bi wɔ Havard ne Duke University.

== Nwuma ==
Mends de ne ho kɔdɔɔm adwumakuo a ɛde Finance Ministry no bre a na ɔreyɛ National Service, wɔ afe 1991 mu na efiri saa bre no besi nnɛ, w'akura dibea ahorɔw pii a emu bi ne otitenani a ɔhwɛ The Americas Desk wɔ afe 1998 mu, Otitenani a ɔda Budget Development ano wɔ afe 2006, ekuo anɔ titenani a ɔda Public Financial Managemnet reform ano wɔ afe 2013 mu. Wɔ bosome a ɛtɔ so nnum no mu wo afe 2017 mu no, wopaw no sɛ ɔkwankyerɛfo a ɔda sikasɛm ho ntotoe ano wɔ adwumakuo a ɛde Ministry Of Finance,dibea a okurae kosii afe 2019 mu. Wonim no se obi a ɔboa maa nsakrae ahorɔw kɔɔ so a emu bi ne Gender responsive Budgeting, Programs Base Budgeting ne Public Financial Management Act foforo a ewɔ hɔ no. Sesie, ɔyɛ ɔkwankyerɛfo a ɔhwɛ ntotoe so wɔ Ministry of Finance. 

